 and the visual style of individual Japanese films and filmmakers.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aMotion picture musiczJapan. 0aMotion pictureszJapanxHistory and criticism. 0aSound in motion pictures. 4aCultural Studies. 4aEast Asia and North East Asia. 4aFilm, Media and Communication. 4aHistory of Film. 4aRadio and Television. 7aHISTORY / Asia / Japan.2bisacsh  aMedia history, transition to sound, cultural history, sound culture.1 aChie, Niita, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFumiaki, Itakura, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKeiko, Sasagawa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aManabu, Ueda, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNordström, Johan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNordström, Johan, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRaine, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRaine, Michael, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aShuhei, Hosokawa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aYohei, Nagato, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311068955608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2021 Englishz978311075408708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyt